recommendations.title: Fix broken event handlers
recommendations.description: These prevent user interactions from working. Add missing function definitions or remove unused event handlers.

recommendations.description: These query non-existent elements. Add missing HTML elements, update JavaScript to use correct IDs, or remove orphaned code.

recommendations.title: Add handlers to interactive elements
recommendations.description: These elements appear clickable but do nothing. Add event handlers or remove unnecessary elements.

recommendations.title: Remove unused functions
recommendations.description: These increase bundle size unnecessarily. Review and remove dead code to improve maintainability.
